data.description: Are you looking for a home that's ready to go? This is it!! This great 3 bed 2 bath home with bonus den has had a new roof 8-20, new carpet throughout 6-20, and foundation repaired 11-20! We even have an inspection from 2020! With an inviting covered porch entry, sprinkler system, and cozy backyard, this could be the home you've been looking for, with all the hard work already done! The large living room has plenty of room for entertainment, along with the bonus den that has built in shelves and a fireplace! Three large bedrooms, two updated bathrooms, and a one car garage plus carport with extra parking off of the alley makes for plenty of room for friends, family, and gatherings! 24 hour notice for showings.
